data.description:
Live a Town  & Country lifestyle on this over 7 acre property tucked deep off a major throughfare with easy access to interstates.  Built in 1922 this home has had some additons over the years expanding the overall square footage and finishing off the marjority of the basement, but still provides plenty of storage space. Current owner just refinished 
 the hardwood floors on the main floor and new carpet was installed in the basement. Blinds and new gutters have also been installed. Main floor is spacious with 2 bedrooms on 1 side and a 3 primary bedroom on the other side for maximum privacey.  Kitchen is spacwious with a large island workspace and fantastic view of the acreage out the kitchen windows. You can also relax on the deck overlooking the acreage while enjoying your morning coffee or happy hour cheer! Property is partially fenced with a privacey fence creating a secure backyard for pets and/or little ones. Plenty of space behind the house for a hobby farm, vineyard or even additional buildings.
